column6: THE DEEP END PART 5 Deadpool isn't getting paid to deliver a prisoner-he's getting paid to take Logan out, once and for all. But is that even possible? Deadpool has found a way, but just as he's about to pull the trigger...a trap springs!
column8: | penciller (cover):Simone Bianchi | inker:Steve Dillon | colorist:Matt Milla | letterer:Cory Petit | writer:Daniel Way
